#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Apache Polaris is powered by Quarkus"
msgstr "阿帕奇北极星由 Quarkus 提供动力"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Apache Polaris, the open-source Iceberg catalog, graduated to an Apache Top-Level Project with Quarkus as its cloud-native foundation. Discover how Polaris leverages Quarkus for performance, extensibility, and developer productivity."
msgstr "开源冰山目录 Apache Polaris 已升级为 Apache 顶级项目，其云原生基础是 Quarkus。了解 Polaris 如何利用 Quarkus 提高性能、可扩展性和开发人员的工作效率。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://polaris.apache.org/[Apache Polaris], an open-source catalog for https://iceberg.apache.org/[Apache Iceberg] has officially graduated to become a Top-Level Project (TLP), capping its incubation with a pivotal technical decision: adopting Quarkus as its cloud-native foundation. The fusion of an Iceberg catalog with Supersonic Subatomic Java delivers not only cloud-native efficiency and extensibility but also community collaboration, positioning Polaris as the leading solution for multi-engine data lakehouse architectures."
msgstr "link:https://polaris.apache.org/[Apache Polaris] 是 link:https://iceberg.apache.org/[Apache Iceberg] 的开源目录，已正式升级为顶级项目 (TLP)，其孵化期结束时做出了一项关键的技术决定：采用 Quarkus 作为其云原生基础。冰山目录与超音速亚原子 Java 的融合不仅带来了云原生的效率和可扩展性，还带来了社区协作，使 Polaris 成为多引擎数据湖架构的领先解决方案。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Journey to Top-Level Project"
msgstr "顶级项目之旅"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Apache Polaris has achieved a major milestone: graduating from the Apache Incubator to become a new Top-Level Project (TLP) within the Apache Software Foundation (ASF). This graduation signifies not only the maturity and community adoption of the project but also its successful integration into the _Apache Way_ of governance and operation."
msgstr "Apache Polaris 实现了一个重要的里程碑：从 Apache 孵化器毕业，成为 Apache 软件基金会（ASF）内一个新的顶级项目（TLP）。此次毕业不仅标志着项目的成熟和社区的采纳，也标志着项目成功融入了 _阿帕奇的_ 管理和运作方式。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Understanding the Apache Incubator"
msgstr "了解阿帕奇孵化器"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The https://incubator.apache.org/[Apache Incubator] is the entry point for projects, known as \"podlings,\" seeking to join the ASF. It guides them through the adoption of meritocratic, consensus-based governance, with experienced mentors acting as liaisons between the podling and the foundation's teams. Polaris successfully completed this mentored incubation process, demonstrating both community maturity and operational readiness."
msgstr "link:https://incubator.apache.org/[阿帕奇孵化器] 是寻求加入 ASF 的项目（称为 \"podlings\"）的切入点。它指导项目采用任人唯贤、协商一致的管理方式，并由经验丰富的导师担任 podling 与基金会团队之间的联络人。北极星成功完成了这一指导孵化过程，展示了社区的成熟度和运营准备就绪程度。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Technical Evolution During Incubation"
msgstr "孵化期间的技术演变"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Polaris, the incubation period was not merely an exercise in governance; it also spurred significant technical development and strategic pivots. The project demonstrated its adaptability and commitment to robust architecture by implementing several important changes, including:"
msgstr "对 Polaris 来说，孵化期不仅仅是一项治理工作，它还促进了重要的技术发展和战略转移。该项目通过实施几项重要变革，展示了其适应能力和对稳健架构的承诺，其中包括"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A New JDBC Persistence Layer: Enhancing the reliability and flexibility of catalog metadata storage and configuration management."
msgstr "新的 JDBC 持久层：提高目录元数据存储和配置管理的可靠性和灵活性"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Advanced Security Features: Integrating new security capabilities, notably through the implementation of the Open Policy Agent (OPA) for policy-based catalog access control, and a sophisticated authorizer framework."
msgstr "高级安全功能：集成新的安全功能，特别是通过实施开放式策略代理（OPA）来实现基于策略的目录访问控制，以及复杂的授权框架。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Robust Policy Management: Developing comprehensive frameworks for defining and enforcing catalog access policies and permissions, a core capability for multi-tenant catalog deployments."
msgstr "强大的策略管理：开发用于定义和执行目录访问策略和权限的综合框架，这是多租户目录部署的核心能力。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Crucially, the team recognized that a successful TLP required a future-proof technical core, which led to one of its most pivotal architectural decisions: adopting Quarkus."
msgstr "最重要的是，该团队认识到，成功的 TLP 需要一个面向未来的技术核心，因此做出了一个最关键的架构决定：采用 Quarkus。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Adoption"
msgstr "夸克斯领养"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Among these technical advancements, one of the most pivotal and forward-looking decisions made during the incubation phase was the **adoption of Quarkus** to power Apache Polaris. This strategic shift recognized that a modern Iceberg catalog serving multiple query engines requires more than traditional Java frameworks could efficiently deliver. The team needed a technology stack that could meet the demanding requirements of cloud-native deployments while maintaining the developer productivity essential for rapid innovation."
msgstr "在这些技术进步中，孵化阶段做出的最关键、最具前瞻性的决定之一就是 *采用 Quarkus* 为 Apache Polaris 提供动力。这一战略转移认识到，为多个查询引擎提供服务的现代冰山目录所需的资源远远超过传统 Java 框架所能有效提供的资源。团队需要一种技术堆栈，既能满足云原生部署的苛刻要求，又能保持开发人员对快速创新至关重要的生产力。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus represents a fundamental shift in how Java applications are built for modern cloud environments. For Apache Polaris, an Iceberg catalog designed to serve multiple query engines, Quarkus provides the ideal combination of performance, developer productivity, and architectural flexibility."
msgstr "Quarkus 标志着为现代云环境构建 Java 应用程序的方式发生了根本性转变。对于 Apache Polaris（一个旨在为多个查询引擎提供服务的冰山目录）来说，Quarkus 提供了性能、开发人员生产力和架构灵活性的理想组合。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Container-First Architecture"
msgstr "容器优先架构"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus was designed from the ground up with a container-first philosophy. Unlike traditional frameworks that were retrofitted for containers, Quarkus optimizes applications specifically for containerized environments by shifting heavy computational work, such as classpath scanning, configuration loading, and dependency injection, from runtime to build time."
msgstr "Quarkus从设计之初就秉承了容器优先的理念。与为容器改造的传统框架不同，Quarkus 通过将繁重的计算工作（如类路径扫描、配置加载和依赖注入）从运行时转移到构建时，专门针对容器化环境优化应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Polaris, this means:"
msgstr "对于北极星来说，这意味着"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Faster Horizontal Scaling**: When deploying additional catalog instances to handle traffic spikes, containers start in milliseconds rather than seconds."
msgstr "*更快的横向扩展* ：在部署额外目录实例以处理流量峰值时，容器以毫秒为单位启动，而不是以秒为单位。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Higher Density**: Lower memory footprint allows more Polaris instances per node, reducing infrastructure costs."
msgstr "*密度更高* ：内存占用更低，每个节点可容纳更多 Polaris 实例，从而降低基础架构成本。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Efficient Resource Use**: Minimal CPU and memory consumption directly lowers operational cloud costs and provides sustainability benefits by reducing resource consumption."
msgstr "*高效利用资源* ：最低的 CPU 和内存消耗可直接降低云计算的运营成本，并通过减少资源消耗带来可持续发展优势。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Performance Characteristics"
msgstr "性能特点"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus delivers performance through four key dimensions:"
msgstr "Quarkus 通过四个关键方面提供性能："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Fast Startup Times:** By performing application initialization work at build time, Quarkus enables Polaris to start rapidly, critical for auto-scaling scenarios where catalog instances must spin up quickly to handle bursts of metadata requests from Spark, Trino, Flink, or other query engines. To give some numbers, canonical Quarkus applications start in 10ms in native mode, in ~100ms using AOT (Leyden), and in 1 to 3s in plain JVM mode."
msgstr "*快速启动时间：* 通过在构建时执行应用初始化工作，Quarkus 使 Polaris 能够快速启动，这对于自动扩展场景至关重要，在这种场景中，目录实例必须快速启动，以处理来自 Spark、Trino、Flink 或其他查询引擎的突发元数据请求。举例来说，典型的 Quarkus 应用程序在本机模式下启动时间为 10 毫秒，使用 AOT（Leyden）模式启动时间约为 100 毫秒，而在纯 JVM 模式下启动时间为 1 到 3 秒。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Reduced Memory Footprint**: The reactive core uses a small number of event loops instead of maintaining large thread pools, dramatically reducing memory usage and enabling higher deployment density."
msgstr "*减少内存占用* ：反应式内核使用少量事件循环，而不是维护大型线程池，从而大大减少了内存使用量，提高了部署密度。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**High Throughput**: The reactive, non-blocking engine based on Netty and Eclipse Vert.x enables Polaris to efficiently process numerous concurrent catalog operations, minimizing blocking during I/O to metadata stores or object storage. This non-blocking, reactive architecture allows Polaris to handle thousands of concurrent client connections, such as metadata requests from Spark or Trino, without dedicating a thread per request, thus avoiding thread-contention bottlenecks."
msgstr "*高吞吐量* ：基于 Netty 和 Eclipse Vert.x 的反应式非阻塞引擎使 Polaris 能够高效处理大量并发目录操作，最大限度地减少元数据存储或对象存储的 I/O 阻塞。这种非阻塞、反应式架构使 Polaris 能够处理成千上万个并发客户端连接，如来自 Spark 或 Trino 的元数据请求，而无需为每个请求专用一个线程，从而避免了线程保留瓶颈。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Optimized Resource Consumption**: The combination of build-time optimization and reactive architecture results in lower CPU requirements, directly reducing cloud costs for organizations running Polaris at scale."
msgstr "*优化资源消耗* ：构建时间优化与反应式架构相结合，降低了 CPU 需求，直接降低了大规模运行 Polaris 的企业的云成本。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Developer Productivity and Versatility"
msgstr "开发人员的生产力和多功能性"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus provides a cohesive, full-stack framework with a rich ecosystem of extensions, enabling the Polaris community to focus on catalog features rather than assembling infrastructure plumbing."
msgstr "Quarkus 提供了一个具有丰富扩展生态系统的内聚全栈框架，使 Polaris 社区能够专注于目录功能，而不是组装基础设施管道。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Frictionless Development Experience:_ The live coding feature provides instant feedback during development, dramatically accelerating the inner development loop and enabling faster iteration on catalog capabilities and security enhancements."
msgstr "_无障碍开发体验：_ 实时编码功能可在开发过程中提供即时反馈，大大加快了内部开发循环，并能更快地迭代目录功能和安全增强功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Programming Model Flexibility:_ Quarkus supports three execution approaches: plain imperative code, reactive programming using the Mutiny API, and virtual threads (JDK 21+), allowing developers to choose the right model for each component. This versatility means Polaris developers can use familiar imperative patterns for simple management endpoints (such as health checks) while fully leveraging the reactive/non-blocking approach (with Mutiny or virtual threads) for high-concurrency, I/O-intensive catalog operations (such as metadata lookups and commits)."
msgstr "_编程模式灵活：_ Quarkus 支持三种执行方法：纯命令式代码、使用 Mutiny API 的反应式编程和虚拟线程（JDK 21+），允许开发人员为每个组件选择合适的模式。这种灵活性意味着 Polaris 开发人员可以使用熟悉的命令式模式来处理简单的管理端点（如健康检查），同时充分利用反应式/无阻塞方法（使用 Mutiny 或虚拟线程）来处理高并发、I/O 密集型目录操作（如元数据查找和提交）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_Protocol Diversity:_ Native support for REST, gRPC, GraphQL, and message brokers (Kafka, RabbitMQ, Pulsar, Apache ActiveMQ) gives Polaris flexibility in how it exposes catalog APIs and integrates with the broader data ecosystem."
msgstr "_协议多样性：_ 对 REST、gRPC、GraphQL 和消息代理（Kafka、RabbitMQ、Pulsar、Apache ActiveMQ）的本地支持使 Polaris 能够灵活地公开目录 API 并与更广泛的数据生态系统集成。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Power of the Quarkiverse Ecosystem"
msgstr "夸克宇宙生态系统的力量"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Beyond the core framework, Quarkus offers access to the **Quarkiverse**, an ecosystem of hundreds of community-driven and vendor-supported extensions. Rather than building custom integrations, the Polaris team leverages battle-tested extensions for persistence (PostgreSQL, MongoDB), security (OIDC, OPA), and observability (OpenTelemetry, Micrometer), as the next section illustrates with concrete examples from the codebase."
msgstr "除核心框架外，Quarkus 还提供对 *Quarkiverse* 的访问权限，这是一个由数百个社区驱动和供应商支持的扩展组成的生态系统。Polaris 团队没有构建自定义集成，而是利用久经考验的扩展来实现持久性（PostgreSQL、MongoDB）、安全性（OIDC、OPA）和可观测性（OpenTelemetry、Micrometer），下一节将通过代码库中的具体示例来说明这一点。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "How Polaris Leverages Quarkus"
msgstr "北极星如何利用 Quarkus"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The true power of the Quarkus foundation becomes evident when examining how Apache Polaris leverages specific Quarkus features in its implementation. The catalog service integrates over 15 specialized extensions to deliver a production-ready, cloud-native Iceberg catalog. Here are a few examples of integration."
msgstr "当研究 Apache Polaris 如何在其实施中利用特定的 Quarkus 功能时，Quarkus 基础的真正威力就显而易见了。该目录服务集成了超过 15 种专业扩展，以提供生产就绪、云原生的 Iceberg 目录。以下是几个集成示例。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Reactive Request Processing with Quarkus REST"
msgstr "使用 Quarkus REST 进行反应式请求处理"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Polaris implements the Iceberg REST API using Quarkus REST, leveraging the Quarkus Reactive Core and SmallRye Mutiny to process thousands of concurrent metadata requests asynchronously without blocking threads."
msgstr "Polaris 使用 Quarkus REST 实现了 Iceberg REST API，利用 Quarkus Reactive Core 和 SmallRye Mutiny 异步处理数千个并发元数据请求，而不会阻塞线程。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here's the actual realm context resolver from the Polaris codebase:"
msgstr "下面是 Polaris 代码库中的实际领域上下文解析器："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With just a few lines of reactive code, Polaris achieves multi-tenant request routing that would typically require significantly more boilerplate in traditional frameworks."
msgstr "只需几行反应代码，Polaris 就能实现多租户请求路由，而传统框架通常需要更多的模板。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Resilience with SmallRye Fault Tolerance"
msgstr "利用 SmallRye 容错技术提高复原力"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For critical operations such as persisting catalog events, Polaris uses Quarkus Fault Tolerance (which relies on SmallRye Fault Tolerance) to ensure reliability. Here is an example of how Polaris implements a resilient flush operation to the metadata store:"
msgstr "对于持久化目录事件等关键操作，Polaris 使用 Quarkus 容错机制（依赖于 SmallRye 容错机制）来确保可靠性。下面举例说明 Polaris 如何实现对元数据存储的弹性刷新操作："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This declarative approach to resilience means Polaris automatically retries failed writes to the metadata store, with configurable backoff and jitter to prevent thundering herd problems. Note that all the configured values can be overridden in the application configuration."
msgstr "这种声明式的弹性方法意味着 Polaris 会自动重试写入元数据存储的失败操作，并通过可配置的回退和抖动来防止雷群问题。请注意，所有配置值都可以在应用配置中重写。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using CDI beans as extension points: selecting the persistence layer"
msgstr "使用 CDI Bean 作为扩展点：选择持久层"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Polaris supports multiple persistence backends (PostgreSQL via the Quarkus JDBC PostgreSQL extension, MongoDB via the Quarkus MongoDB Client extension, and in-memory for testing) using Quarkus's CDI qualifier mechanism:"
msgstr "Polaris 利用 Quarkus 的 CDI 限定符机制支持多种持久性后端（通过 Quarkus JDBC PostgreSQL 扩展的 PostgreSQL、通过 Quarkus MongoDB Client 扩展的 MongoDB 以及用于测试的内存）："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This architecture allows operators to deploy Polaris with the persistence layer that matches their infrastructure requirements, simply by changing the `polaris.persistence.nosql.backend` configuration property."
msgstr "通过这种架构，操作员只需更改 `polaris.persistence.nosql.backend` 配置属性，即可使用符合其基础设施要求的持久层部署 Polaris。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Comprehensive Observability"
msgstr "全面可观测性"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Polaris leverages Quarkus Micrometer with Prometheus registry and Quarkus OpenTelemetry for complete observability. The catalog automatically tracks:"
msgstr "Polaris 利用 Quarkus Micrometer、Prometheus 注册表和 Quarkus OpenTelemetry 实现全面观测。目录自动跟踪"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**HTTP metrics** for all Iceberg REST API requests, tagged by realm, operation, and status code"
msgstr "所有冰山 REST API 请求的 *HTTP 指标* ，按领域、操作和状态代码标记"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Custom gauges and counters** for catalog-specific metrics like table count, namespace count, and metadata operation latency"
msgstr "针对表计数、命名空间计数和元数据操作延迟等特定目录指标的 *自定义仪表和计数器*"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Distributed traces** that follow requests across catalog operations, from initial metadata request through to storage access"
msgstr "*分布式跟踪* 可跟踪整个目录操作过程中的请求，从最初的元数据请求一直到存储访问"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The metrics endpoint is exposed on a separate management port (8182), isolated from the main API port (8181), following Kubernetes best practices:"
msgstr "按照 Kubernetes 最佳实践，度量端点暴露在一个单独的管理端口（8182）上，与主 API 端口（8181）隔离："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Collaboration between Quarkus and Polaris Communities"
msgstr "Quarkus 和 Polaris 社区之间的合作"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The adoption of Quarkus has created a productive feedback loop between the two communities. Engineers from both projects have worked closely together to ensure Quarkus is used effectively within Polaris, reporting bugs and identifying possible enhancements along the way. This hands-on collaboration benefits both sides: Polaris gets a solid, well-understood foundation, while Quarkus gains real-world feedback from a demanding, high-throughput Apache TLP deployment, driving stability and performance improvements that benefit the entire Quarkus ecosystem."
msgstr "Quarkus 的采用在两个社区之间形成了一个富有成效的反馈回路。两个项目的工程师密切合作，确保 Quarkus 在 Polaris 中得到有效使用，同时报告错误并确定可能的改进。这种亲身实践的合作使双方都受益匪浅：Polaris 获得了坚实、易懂的基础，而 Quarkus 则从高要求、高吞吐量的 Apache TLP 部署中获得了实际反馈，推动了稳定性和性能的提高，使整个 Quarkus 生态系统受益。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Looking Ahead"
msgstr "展望未来"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The successful graduation of Apache Polaris as a Top-Level Project, combined with the power and efficiency gained from its foundation on Quarkus, is merely the launchpad for a significant, forward-looking technical agenda. Polaris is positioned not just for growth, but to actively shape the future of cloud-native data lakehouse architectures."
msgstr "Apache Polaris 成功升级为顶级项目，再加上其在 Quarkus 基础上获得的强大功能和效率，这仅仅是一个重要的前瞻性技术议程的启动平台。Polaris 的定位不仅仅是增长，而是积极塑造云原生数据湖架构的未来。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The community is already aligning its development with the cutting edge of the Quarkus roadmap, including the forthcoming Quarkus 4 major release. This alignment guarantees that Polaris will continually benefit from performance gains, new cloud-native APIs, and the most advanced capabilities for its reactive core."
msgstr "该社区已将其开发与 Quarkus 路线图的最前沿保持一致，包括即将发布的 Quarkus 4 主要版本。这种协调保证了 Polaris 将持续受益于性能提升、新的云原生 API 以及反应式内核的最先进功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Our vision extends to embracing new networking and security standards to meet the demands of the most critical deployments:"
msgstr "我们的愿景还包括采用新的网络和安全标准，以满足最关键的部署需求："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Next-Generation Networking:** We are exploring the adoption of HTTP/3, leveraging its multiplexing and reduced head-of-line blocking to further minimize latency and boost the throughput of metadata requests, which is crucial for query engines managing thousands of concurrent operations."
msgstr "*下一代网络：* 我们正在探索采用 HTTP/3，利用其多路复用功能和减少的线头阻塞，进一步减少延迟并提高元数据请求的吞吐量，这对于管理数千个并发操作的查询引擎至关重要。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Future-Proof Security:** Looking beyond today's standards, the project is investigating quantum-safe TLS and encryption. By integrating modern cryptographic practices, Polaris aims to provide a catalog that is secure not just for the present, but against the computational challenges of the future."
msgstr "*面向未来的安全：* 该项目着眼于当今的标准之外，正在研究量子安全 TLS 和加密。通过整合现代密码学实践，北极星旨在提供一个不仅对当前安全，而且能应对未来计算挑战的目录。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-24-quarkus-polaris.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This commitment to continuous innovation, driven by an active community, ensures that Apache Polaris is ready to become the industry standard for high-performance, secure, and multi-engine Iceberg catalog interoperability. We welcome contributors, users, and organizations to join us in defining this next era of the data ecosystem."
msgstr "在活跃社区的推动下，我们致力于不断创新，确保 Apache Polaris 成为高性能、安全和多引擎冰山目录互操作性的行业标准。我们欢迎贡献者、用户和组织与我们一起定义数据生态系统的下一个时代。"
